  <brief_title>Postoperative Analgesic Effects of Using Dexmedetomidine for Ultrasound Guided Thoracic Paravertebral Block</brief_title>
  <official_title>Postoperative Analgesic Effects of Using Bupivacaine Alone or Added Dexmedetomidine for Ultrasound Guided Thoracic Paravertebral Block in Thoracotomy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
